{"tid":1967823,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解放軍第一艘075兩棲攻擊艦疑艤裝期間失火濃煙沖天","createTime":"2020-04-11T08:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T11:25:05.000Z","uid":28765,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ae6fdbd58f587cebbfa82cdc635ac70d4c7f69c1","tid":1967823,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T08:01:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/04/11/phpXklW2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F04%2F11%2FphpXklW2b.jpg&h=307ba448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國解放軍首艘075型兩棲攻擊艦，自去年9月25日下水後目前正在艤裝（靠岸裝配），孰料今天（11日）突然傳出起火意外，現場不僅濃煙沖天，大火熄滅後還可以看到船尾被燒得焦黑。<br />\n<br />\n百度貼吧「航空母艦吧」今上午有網友PO出了075型兩棲攻擊艦火燒船的照片，只見軍艦從船中央至尾部皆冒出濃煙，消息傳到微博後曾引起一番討論，但迅速被控制言論，目前微博上已找不到相關消息。<br />\n<br />\n「航空母艦吧」接著又出現了1張照片，只見075型兩棲攻擊艦在撲滅火勢後，船尾已被燒得一片焦黑，讓中國網友紛紛擔心軍艦內部不知燒得怎麼樣了，還有人認為按照這樣的火勢來看，恐怕裝配工程要延遲1年以上了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/04/11/phpX3O4MC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F04%2F11%2FphpX3O4MC.jpg&h=3564b0d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大火熄滅後，可以看到075型兩棲攻擊艦船尾被燒得焦黑。（圖擷自百度貼吧）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3130487\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3130487&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=23a2b765\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3130487&h=469d7c7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3130487</a>"},{"pid":"9e3094b46c958d1c05f952312fd3403140d36cc9","tid":1967823,"uid":7355,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T08:02:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><